response.original_title: Four the movie: The Final Chapter
response.overview: After Kanye west terrorizes the world with a nuke called “Donda 3” The movie holics are on a ticking clock and prepare for one last adventure. Four tries to find himself and find his brother. Emoji teams up with an old friend tarry t and is on the run from Jayden. And one old friend of the movie holics is behind it all.
response.tagline: Saving the universe once and FOUR all
